<h2>1.3Â Â  How much time will be taken by the RPC for QC?</h2>
At RPC, every item will be quality checked thoroughly to validate customer complaint. The RPC will take a maximum ofÂ <strong>72Â hours</strong>Â to process the shipments.
<h2>1.4Â Â  What if my item is â€˜QC failedâ€™ at RPC?</h2>
