If the item is QC failed at RPC, we will not send the item back to the merchant and the item will be liquidated from the RPC. The status of such items will be shown as â€˜Liquidatedâ€™ in the â€˜Returnsâ€™ tab of Seller panel. No debit will be marked to the merchant in such cases.

