<h2>1.6Â Â  What if I want my shipment to be assigned to an RPC?</h2>
The prerogative of mapping a merchant to the RPC/sending a shipment to the RPC shall lie with Paytm. A merchant can raise a request to process his/her shipments through the RPC via merchant helpdesk (email: <a href="mailto:merchant.helpdesk@paytm.com">merchant.helpdesk@paytm.com</a>) but Paytmâ€™s decision in this regard shall be final.
<h2>1.7Â Â  When will I receive my product if it is QC passed?</h2>
Once the Item has passed the quality check and has been shipped from RPC, the merchant will get a notification about the shipments dispatched through an email. The merchant should receive such item(s) at their warehouse within 21 days of reverse pickup from the customer.

